Home Page
Your investment opportunity
Strategic Storage Trust II, Inc. is a public non-traded REIT focused on the self storage industry. Self storage is an asset class driven by human life factors such as birth, death, marriage, divorce, retirement, relocation, military enlistment, economic expansion and contraction. We believe that SST2 can provide stability, diversification, income and the potential for growth over the long term.(1)
 
