Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Real Estate
Sub-Industry: REIT
Strategic Storage Trust II, Inc. operates as a real estate investment trust. The Company invests primarily in a portfolio of income-producing self storage facilities and related self storage real estate investments. Strategic Storage Trust II conducts business in the United States.




