        Strategic Storage Trust

























 
On June 15, 2015 - SmartStop Self Storage, Inc. announced it has entered into a definitive merger agreement under which it will be acquired by Extra Space Storage Inc. (NYSE: EXR). SmartStop stockholders will receive $13.75 per share in cash which represents a total purchase price of $1.4 billion.
 









