About SSTI



About SSTI
Strategic Storage Trust, Inc. is the fifth public self storage company in the United States and the first self storage REIT in the public non-traded REIT marketplace. The self storage industry is a unique asset class which displays recession-resistant traits as it is affected by human life factors such as marriage, divorce, retirement, relocation, and military enlistment. This, combined with a fragmented industry and baby boomer demographics, makes for an attractive real estate asset class in the coming years.
The Strategic Storage Trust, Inc. management team is comprised of industry veterans. They have institutional experience in the underwriting and acquisitions of self storage properties. Collectively, our team has over 50 years of self storage experience and has completed over $10 billion in real estate transactions. 












